#: app/templates/legal.html:10
msgid ""
"Please read these Terms of Service (\"Terms\") carefully before using the"
" https://pictotree.eu website (the \"Service\") operated by the "
"Pictotree.eu team (\"us\", \"we\", or \"our\")."
